824
00:29:13,620 --> 00:29:16,260
Okay, so it's called Dust because we, like,

825
00:29:16,260 --> 00:29:20,640
came from dust, man, and that's the intro.

826
00:29:20,640 --> 00:29:22,520
You'd think they'd explain a little bit more

