watch Avatar The Last Airbender.

2680
01:34:13,200 --> 01:34:15,200
Oh, this explains a lot of things.

2681
01:34:15,200 --> 01:34:17,200
Once you go watch Avatar, you start to realize

2682
01:34:17,200 --> 01:34:19,200
