2686
01:34:26,200 --> 01:34:28,200
RWBY has four kingdoms,

2687
01:34:28,200 --> 01:34:29,200
so you see it's different.

2688
01:34:29,200 --> 01:34:31,200
The four kingdoms.

2689
01:34:31,200 --> 01:34:33,200
They're called kingdoms because, well,

2690
01:34:33,200 --> 01:34:34,200
