2708
01:35:11,200 --> 01:35:12,200
You see, it's actually a clever twist

2709
01:35:12,200 --> 01:35:14,200
because no one would have expected them

2710
01:35:14,200 --> 01:35:15,200
to be that obvious,

2711
01:35:15,200 --> 01:35:18,200
so when they really did just do Avatar again,

2712
01:35:18,200 --> 01:35:19,200
it's a genuine surprise.

